Package ie.atu.sw

Class VirtualThreadFileParser

java.lang.Object
ie.atu.sw.VirtualThreadFileParser
Direct Known Subclasses:
FileCollector
public abstract class VirtualThreadFileParser extends Object
Since:
JavaSE-19 VirtualThreadFileParser is an abstract class. The function of this class is to parse text files and CSV files using virtual threads. Citations: (Ireeder 2014; Healy 2022a, 2022b; Lee 2022).
